      "text": "This Great Big Story was made possible by Wells Fargo."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3000.0,
      "end_time": 6000.0,
      "text": "Established 1852. Re-Established 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7380.0,
      "end_time": 10911.0,
      "text": "(wolves howling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10912.0,
      "end_time": 12701.0,
      "text": "There's something about being part of nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12701.0,
      "end_time": 14992.0,
      "text": "there's something about being around these animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14992.0,
      "end_time": 16491.0,
      "text": "To even the most wounded veteran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16491.0,
      "end_time": 18141.0,
      "text": "they feel different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18141.0,
      "end_time": 22670.0,
      "text": "keeps them part of something greater than themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22680.0,
      "end_time": 24818.0,
      "text": "(wolves howling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 27766.0,
      "end_time": 31154.0,
      "text": "The idea is that you've gotta give someone who's been"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31155.0,
      "end_time": 35683.0,
      "text": "through a severe trauma, an opportunity to heal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35683.0,
      "end_time": 38750.0,
      "text": "and we believe that Warriors and Wolves program"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38750.0,
      "end_time": 40991.0,
      "text": "in a back to nature setting, it does that."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40991.0,
      "end_time": 43694.0,
      "text": "We have 40 animals at this facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43694.0,
      "end_time": 45105.0,
      "text": "There you go, you got it."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 45105.0,
      "end_time": 45995.0,
      "text": "You'll get that."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45995.0,
      "end_time": 48665.0,
      "text": "[Matthew] We've rescued wolves off of chains in Alaska"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48665.0,
      "end_time": 50425.0,
      "text": "as part of a roadside attraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50425.0,
      "end_time": 54774.0,
      "text": "We rescued wolf dogs from a backyard breeder in San Diego."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54774.0,
      "end_time": 56644.0,
      "text": "I think for all the veterans that we bring out here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56644.0,
      "end_time": 59443.0,
      "text": "whether they work here or they're here for a support group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59443.0,
      "end_time": 63443.0,
      "text": "what rings true is if they can heal, I can heal."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65710.0,
      "end_time": 66902.0,
      "text": "- The wolves, they notice you're injured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66902.0,
      "end_time": 68222.0,
      "text": "or something's wrong with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68222.0,
      "end_time": 69642.0,
      "text": "and they have that trauma."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69642.0,
      "end_time": 72420.0,
      "text": "So, you know, we had some type of trauma in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72430.0,
      "end_time": 73982.0,
      "text": "we kinda get that connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 73982.0,
      "end_time": 77809.0,
      "text": "and one wolf will be your friend for life."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77809.0,
      "end_time": 79759.0,
      "text": "- [Matthew] What happens is one animal"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79759.0,
      "end_time": 81483.0,
      "text": "picks that one veteran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81483.0,
      "end_time": 84330.0,
      "text": "never again does that animal pick someone else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84330.0,
      "end_time": 85611.0,
      "text": "never again does that animal want to show"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 85611.0,
      "end_time": 87971.0,
      "text": "the same kind of affection to someone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87971.0,
      "end_time": 89937.0,
      "text": "- What a good boy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 89937.0,
      "end_time": 93708.0,
      "text": "Conventional therapy isn't really something for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93708.0,
      "end_time": 95319.0,
      "text": "It didn't help to be honest."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 95319.0,
      "end_time": 97986.0,
      "text": "After 10 years of military life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 99870.0,
      "end_time": 101319.0,
      "text": "it was sort of a tough transition."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101319.0,
      "end_time": 105152.0,
      "text": "Had I continued down my course of being angry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106980.0,
      "end_time": 107554.0,
      "text": "drinking myself to death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107554.0,
      "end_time": 111540.0,
      "text": "may have been the last chapter of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115789.0,
      "end_time": 118359.0,
      "text": "- There are things I've seen that I can't unsee."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118359.0,
      "end_time": 121286.0,
      "text": "There are things I've done that I cannot undo."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121287.0,
      "end_time": 124278.0,
      "text": "Just saying that, well I did it in the name of my country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124278.0,
      "end_time": 126960.0,
      "text": "doesn't help you sleep at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126960.0,
      "end_time": 129125.0,
      "text": "But what does help you sleep is having a companion."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129125.0,
      "end_time": 133292.0,
      "text": "- They kinda teach you how to be calm and confident."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135731.0,
      "end_time": 139399.0,
      "text": "It's got some deeper meaning when they accept you."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139399.0,
      "end_time": 143566.0,
      "text": "They accept you into the family, as part of the pack."
    }
  ]
}